A 60-year-old British man has died while watching porn at a sex shop in Italy. According to Dailymail, the man was suspected to have suffered a heart attack while watching a pornographic film in the private booth in a sex top shop Marghera near Venice. The deceased paid five euros for a 15-minute video and shut himself in the booth. READ ALSO: Court orders remand of Sowore, co-defendant in DSS custody The Staff in the Italian sex shop claimed they became concerned when he failed to emerge after 30 minutes and then found him on the floor. Police have confirmed they are investigating the circumstances behind the death of the unnamed man.